<i>♪ Heroes in a half shell ♪</i>

00:12.178 --> 00:13.512
<i>♪ Turtle power ♪</i>

00:13.514 --> 00:14.446
<i>♪ They're the world's ♪</i>

00:14.448 --> 00:16.280
<i>♪ Most fearsome</i>
<i>fighting team ♪</i>

00:16.283 --> 00:18.182
We're really hip.

00:18.184 --> 00:20.385
<i>♪ They're heroes</i>
<i>in the half shell ♪</i>

00:20.387 --> 00:21.753
<i>♪ And they're green ♪</i>

00:21.755 --> 00:23.221
<i>♪ Teenage Mutant</i>
<i>Ninja Turtles ♪</i>
Hey, get a grip.

00:23.223 --> 00:25.723
<i>♪ When the evil Shredder</i>
<i>attacks ♪</i>

00:25.725 --> 00:28.760
<i>♪ These Turtle boys</i>
<i>don't cut him no slack ♪</i>

00:28.762 --> 00:31.529
<i>♪ Teenage Mutant</i>
<i>Ninja Turtles ♪</i>

00:31.531 --> 00:33.965
<i>♪ Teenage Mutant</i>
<i>Ninja Turtles ♪</i>

00:33.967 --> 00:36.868
<i>♪ Splinter taught them</i>
<i>to be ninja teens ♪</i>

